pull_request.title: Limit gcc version supported
pull_request.body:
Replaces #1449 documenting and enforcing minimal gcc version 7.1.0.

pull_request.title: make algorithms selectable by liboqs bitstrength
pull_request.body:
This permits selection of algorithms by bitstrength using [Property query strings](https://www.openssl.org/docs/man3.0/man7/crypto.html), e.g. 

    openssl list -provider oqsprovider -propquery oqsprovider.security_bits=256 -signature-algorithms
